00:32:44,090 --> 00:32:45,220
to get your verdict.

568
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:46,460
For a case like mine,

569
00:32:47,330 --> 00:32:48,740
what are my chances of winning?

570
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:52,060
I understand.

571
00:32:52,460 --> 00:32:53,850
Before the verdict,

572
00:32:54,300 --> 00:32:55,300
nothing's certain.

573
00:32:58,300 --> 00:33:00,330
You and Captain Zhang
have really worked hard.

574
00:33:00,850 --> 00:33:01,820
I'll head back now.

575
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:07,300
Ye Sibei.

576
00:33:11,300 --> 00:33:12,330
For you,

577
00:33:12,930 --> 00:33:14,300
it should be over now.

578
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:16,410
Now that it's in our hands,

579
00:33:16,930 --> 00:33:18,020
we'll put an end to it.

580
00:33:19,090 --> 00:33:20,260
You don't need to stay stuck.

581
00:33:21,410 --> 00:33:22,580
You can look ahead now.

582
00:33:23,650 --> 00:33:24,490
I know.

583
00:33:25,460 --> 00:33:26,980
I'm studying for an exam.

584
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:28,740
I'll be taking the CICPA test.

585
00:33:30,300 --> 00:33:31,140
Thank you.

586
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,170
Take care.

587
00:33:46,220 --> 00:33:47,300
Say what's on your mind.

588
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:52,330
I can't figure it out.

589
00:33:52,330 --> 00:33:53,820
Then stop trying.

590
00:33:54,066 --> 00:33:56,177
That brain of yours
won't figure it out anyway.

591
00:33:58,650 --> 00:33:59,490
Master.

592
00:34:00,060 --> 00:34:01,820
Ye Sibei is clearly the victim.

593
00:34:02,022 --> 00:34:03,860
Why does she have
to put up with all this?

594
00:34:04,650 --> 00:34:05,810
You should've seen

595
00:34:05,810 --> 00:34:07,540
how she covered herself
so tightly just now.

596
00:34:07,540 --> 00:34:10,210
Why do victims have to carry such shame?

597
00:34:10,730 --> 00:34:11,810
What did she do wrong?

598
00:34:11,810 --> 00:34:13,420
Stop asking why.

599
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:15,020
Do you think this is an exam

600
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:17,580
where you write the right answer

601
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:18,460
and get points?

602
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:20,650
What is reality?

603
00:34:21,170 --> 00:34:22,290
What is life?

604
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:25,290
It's when you know the right answer,

605
00:34:25,290 --> 00:34:26,730
but you

606
00:34:26,730 --> 00:34:27,810
can't act

607
00:34:27,810 --> 00:34:28,650
accordingly.

608
00:34:29,222 --> 00:34:30,540
There's no standard answer to it.

609
00:34:30,540 --> 00:34:31,810
That's what reality is.

610
00:35:30,640 --> 00:35:31,355
(The rapist's wife and daughter.)

611
00:35:31,355 --> 00:35:32,210
What are you doing?

612
00:35:32,210 --> 00:35:33,420
Don't block our way!

613
00:35:33,777 --> 00:35:34,490
Move! Go away!

614
00:35:34,610 --> 00:35:35,060
Ms. Chuchu!

615
00:35:35,170 --> 00:35:35,900
Move aside!

616
00:35:35,900 --> 00:35:36,466
Ms. Chuchu!

617
00:35:36,466 --> 00:35:37,770
Don't avoid us, Ms. Chuchu!

618
00:35:37,770 --> 00:35:38,780
(-Ye Nianwen, you heartless vampire.
-How can you still be with her?)

619
00:35:40,940 --> 00:35:41,360
(Huang Guifen, selling out
your daughter...)

620
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:41,780
(Ye Ling, you coward.)

621
00:35:47,380 --> 00:35:49,900
(Alas, girls should really learn
to protect themselves.)

622
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:58,300
(Sibei, stay strong! You're amazing!)

623
00:35:58,300 --> 00:36:00,780
(Believe in yourself.
You're stronger than you think.)

624
00:36:00,780 --> 00:36:01,980
(Be brave. You can do it.)

625
00:36:32,740 --> 00:36:34,860
(Certificate of Merit,
Class Star Student)

626
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:37,300
(2017, 5th Nancheng
Children's Piano Competition)

627
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:49,340
The trial's tomorrow.

628
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:52,130
Mr. Fan has one request.

629
00:36:54,340 --> 00:36:55,860
He told you

630
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,610
to polish Wenwen's trophy often.

631
00:36:57,610 --> 00:36:58,580
It gathers dust easily.

632
00:39:39,290 --> 00:39:40,170
Dinner's ready.

633
00:39:57,290 --> 00:39:58,210
What's wrong?

634
00:40:02,690 --> 00:40:04,170
The trial's tomorrow.

635
00:40:04,730 --> 00:40:06,060
Isn't that a good thing?

636
00:40:08,210 --> 00:40:09,580
Are you nervous?

637
00:40:12,170 --> 00:40:13,210
I'm a little scared.

638
00:40:14,170 --> 00:40:15,020
Sibei.

639
00:40:16,580 --> 00:40:17,860
We've come this far.

640
00:40:19,020 --> 00:40:20,340
There's nothing left to fear.

641
00:40:21,210 --> 00:40:22,060
Besides, I came across

642
00:40:22,060 --> 00:40:23,733
the encouraging notes
from those netizens.

643
00:40:24,690 --> 00:40:26,420
With all of them behind you,

644
00:40:27,020 --> 00:40:28,690
it's Fan Jiancheng who should be scared.

645
00:40:29,610 --> 00:40:31,500
But no one's perfect.

646
00:40:32,170 --> 00:40:33,210
What if they find out

647
00:40:33,210 --> 00:40:35,340
I'm not who they expect me to be?

648
00:40:37,610 --> 00:40:39,020
They'll curse me too, won't they?

649
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:41,500
Stop thinking about it.

650
00:40:42,340 --> 00:40:43,180
Let's eat.

651
00:40:59,580 --> 00:41:00,650
Mommy.

652
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:02,340
Wenwen.

653
00:41:04,170 --> 00:41:05,010
Wenwen.

654
00:41:05,980 --> 00:41:07,860
- Mommy.
- What's it, baby?

655
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:10,940
It's getting late.
Why aren't you in bed?

656
00:41:11,500 --> 00:41:12,340
Why are you crying?

657
00:41:12,340 --> 00:41:13,980
Why aren't you in bed either?

658
00:41:15,250 --> 00:41:17,060
I miss Daddy.

659
00:41:17,810 --> 00:41:20,020
I miss Daddy.

660
00:41:23,290 --> 00:41:25,210
Come here, baby.
Mommy will give you a hug.

661
00:41:25,210 --> 00:41:26,170
Hear me out.

662
00:41:27,500 --> 00:41:28,540
Well,

663
00:41:29,250 --> 00:41:30,090
Daddy...

664
00:41:31,130 --> 00:41:32,730
Daddy has been framed.

665
00:41:32,730 --> 00:41:34,130
He's innocent.

666
00:41:34,940 --> 00:41:37,420
Mr. Policeman will send him home soon.

667
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:38,500
So stop crying,

668
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,340
got it?

669
00:41:40,290 --> 00:41:42,610
But my classmates called Daddy

670
00:41:42,610 --> 00:41:44,540
a baddie.

671
00:41:45,340 --> 00:41:47,020
They were talking nonsense.

672
00:41:47,020 --> 00:41:48,340
There's no way Daddy's a baddie.

673
00:41:48,340 --> 00:41:49,690
He's a good person.

674
00:41:49,690 --> 00:41:51,290
Daddy has been kind to you,

675
00:41:51,290 --> 00:41:52,170
hasn't he?

676
00:41:52,980 --> 00:41:54,810
You've never seen Daddy do evil

677
00:41:54,810 --> 00:41:55,980
or talk bad about anyone,

678
00:41:55,980 --> 00:41:56,820
right?

679
00:41:57,810 --> 00:41:59,090
I promise.

680
00:42:00,130 --> 00:42:00,980
Your dad

681
00:42:00,980 --> 00:42:02,130
will be home soon.

682
00:42:04,170 --> 00:42:05,210
Let me give you a hug.

683
00:42:05,210 --> 00:42:07,060
There, there.

684
00:42:39,160 --> 00:42:45,270
♪Just let the dark night remember♪

685
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:52,940
♪How should I walk toward tomorrow?♪

686
00:42:55,640 --> 00:43:01,900
♪Helpless against the rumors and teases♪

687
00:43:03,720 --> 00:43:10,160
♪Unwilling to yield for the last time♪

688
00:43:12,200 --> 00:43:14,140
♪Who's watching me?♪

689
00:43:14,250 --> 00:43:16,290
♪Who's pulling me?♪

690
00:43:16,290 --> 00:43:18,760
♪Who pushed me away?♪

691
00:43:20,540 --> 00:43:27,040
♪Observing me from a distance♪

692
00:43:28,810 --> 00:43:30,810
♪As I struggle♪

693
00:43:30,810 --> 00:43:32,730
♪Grow weaker♪

694
00:43:32,730 --> 00:43:36,320
♪And fall into desolation♪

695
00:43:36,730 --> 00:43:43,450
♪Banishing me with a mere sentence♪

696
00:43:45,160 --> 00:43:52,440
♪Listen to the deep sea♪

697
00:43:53,300 --> 00:44:01,090
♪Listen to the soundless breathing♪

698
00:44:03,290 --> 00:44:04,650
Can I hug you?

699
00:44:11,170 --> 00:44:12,810
Can I hug you?

700
00:44:52,340 --> 00:44:57,100
♪There's a gray cloud in your eyes♪

701
00:44:59,080 --> 00:45:04,670
♪But I see a long letter
through the clouds♪

702
00:45:05,750 --> 00:45:11,920
♪You hide your emotions, staying silent♪

703
00:45:12,370 --> 00:45:17,440
♪I wish I could accompany you
back to the clear sky♪

704
00:45:18,960 --> 00:45:24,070
♪If I could capture your shadow♪

705
00:45:25,690 --> 00:45:31,040
♪I wouldn't mind wandering again♪

706
00:45:32,300 --> 00:45:38,690
♪Moreover, my light is in your life♪

707
00:45:39,010 --> 00:45:44,450
♪So I must trust in myself♪

708
00:45:45,040 --> 00:45:49,350
♪Please let me become you♪

709
00:45:49,520 --> 00:45:52,980
♪The secret that you can tell♪

710
00:45:52,980 --> 00:45:58,540
♪Becoming the gentle fragrance
that heals your past♪

711
00:45:58,540 --> 00:46:02,540
♪If fate insists on drenching you♪

712
00:46:02,830 --> 00:46:05,580
♪With a torrential downpour♪

713
00:46:05,980 --> 00:46:11,400
♪Don't be afraid, I am your soul's coat♪

714
00:46:11,700 --> 00:46:15,770
♪Please let me become you♪

715
00:46:16,240 --> 00:46:19,550
♪Believing in the proof of love♪

716
00:46:19,550 --> 00:46:25,180
♪Becoming the island
where every dream of yours rests♪

717
00:46:25,180 --> 00:46:29,340
♪Don't lament the lost scenery♪

718
00:46:29,630 --> 00:46:32,280
♪As time passes♪

719
00:46:32,930 --> 00:46:38,200
♪I will still be here♪

720
00:46:38,800 --> 00:46:45,750
♪Not forgetting to accompany you
